-- Rexel Plans to Pay Dividend Next Year If It Lowers Debt, Investir Reports
-- Tara Patel
-- 2010-07-31T09:35:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-31/rexel-plans-to-pay-dividend-next-year-if-it-lowers-debt-investir-reports.html

          
          
             Rexel SA  will pay shareholders a
dividend next year if it lowers its debt,  Investir  reported,
citing an interview with Chairman  Jean-Charles Pauze .  
 The company also wants to cut debt to make acquisitions,
Pauze was quoted as saying.  
